article.description: — Nathan Mensah had 14 points and three blocks as San Diego State got past Air Force 76-64 on Saturday.
article.headline: Mensah carries San Diego St. over Air Force 76-64
article.linkText: Mensah carries San Diego St. over Air Force 76-64
article.story: SAN DIEGO -- — Nathan Mensah had 14 points and three blocks as San Diego State got past Air Force 76-64 on Saturday. Matt Bradley had 13 points for San Diego State (15-6, 7-3 Mountain West Conference), which earned its fourth consecutive home victory. Keshad Johnson added 11 points. A.J. Walker tied a season high with 27 points for the Falcons (10-13, 3-9), who have now lost five games in a row. Nikc Jackson added 13 points. Jake Heidbreder had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
